latestPosts.caption:
IT’S HERE! 🎉 Episode 1 of @youareaforce_podcast is LIVE!

After years of manifesting, months of planning, and beautiful, soul-stirring conversations, I am beyond grateful and thrilled to finally share the very first episode of #YouAreAForce — featuring @namratasoni : the makeup maestro, history-maker, and creative genius behind some of the most iconic faces you’ve ever seen. 💄✨

Namrata is a true force of nature — breaking boundaries in beauty, business, and beyond.

In this episode, we dive into:
✅ Fighting gender barriers in Bollywood 🎥
✅ Building a beauty empire for Indian skin tones 💥 @simplynam.beauty 
✅ Creating legacy with purpose, pigment, and power 🎯

This conversation touched my heart and I can’t wait for you to hear it.

Listen now on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, YouTube, LinkedIn & wherever you get your glow. Link in bio. 🔗✨ #youareaforce #namratasoni #simplynam #womeninbusiness #womensupportingwomen #globalsisterhood
